Mesos can allocate resources for web servers, small scripts and can be used in hadoop
YARN can be integrated with Mesos using Myriad
Cloudera has a distribution with Mesos instead Yarn

Oozie is a tool to create a workflow of jobs in hadoop

Zeppelin is very similar to a iPhython notebook

HUE (Hadoop User Experience): It has the same objective as Apache Ambari summed with Zeppelin. Hue has a Oozie editor. 
